Candidate will be responsible for developing and implementing Android and iOS apps according to provided specifications and mock-ups. The best candidates will have the opportunity to get converted to full-time and granted with equity options. 
Duty - 100% of your work will be mobile app development in native Android and iOS. 
Location - you will be working 100% remotely. There's only one scum teleconference per week that's up to two hours long. All the communications are done via Slack. 
Technology: Android native, Kotlin, Swift 
Workflow - you will be assigned with Jira tickets to work on that contains UI mock-ups, feature description and Definition of Done 
Play Store submission - you will be responsible for publishing the work to Android and iOS app stores 
As a team player - you will be in close collaborations with front-end, back-end and infrastructure engineers to solve technical problems such as scalability, CI/CD, quality control, etc. 
Training - At Nhebo we embrace the knowledge-cross-pollination methodology. Hence, as a member of a highly skilled and specialized engineering team, you are encouraged to share your knowledge and helping others. 
Required Skills: 
- Native iOS 
- Xcode IDE 
- Swift or Objective-C 
- Story boarding – Designs work on iPhone / iPad in landscape and portrait 
- UI Automation Tests, Unit Tests 
- Provisions, Test flight, Certificates 
- Native Android 
- Android Studio 
- Java, Kotlin 
- XML Layout Markup 
- UI Automator Tests, Unit Tests 
Other Experiences: 
- Able to deploy applications to iOS and Android app stores 
- In-App Purchases and Subscriptions 
- Push Notifications, Remote and Local 
- Saving to local storage such as sqlite, core data, settings, etc 
- Can integrate third party SDKs such as facebook, and Gmail, amazon. 
- Can execute a design mockup to interface using xml or designer tools built into each environment. 
- Understands background operations, and threads 
Networking such as calling out to REST services and websockets 
- Clear understanding of limitations, performance of animations, data processing, and effects 
- Knows about app store limitations and requirements for Apple App Store or Google Play such as export laws, encryption, privacy of data, insecure data, etc 
- Must have the ability to follow through, with attention to detail
